data.description: Outside city limits and sitting on .66 of an acre! This well maintained 1578sf 3 bd, 2 ba home is ready & waiting for your family. Cathedral ceilings, breakfast nook/conversation area, dining room, galley style kitchen w/ dbl oven, pantry, & walk-in closet in master. New roof in 2016, AC compressor in 2017 & freshly painted interior along w/ many other updates. Privacy fenced yard w/ mature shade trees, perfect for BBQing w/ friends. Storage building w/ lean-to perfect for your outdoor projects covered.
